      • Cell

        public Cell​(Border b1,
            Border b2,
            Border b3,
            Border b4,
            CellColor color,
            boolean respawner,
            AmmoTile ammoCard,
            int row,
            int column)
        N.B.: this constructor acts only for testing purposes, as all the cell of the game maps are deserialized from json through the default constructor; Constructor: creates a new Cell based on its borders, color, ammo tile, position on the map and whether it is a respawner cell
        Parameters:
        b1 - northern border of the cell, defined as a Border Enum value
        b2 - eastern border of the cell, defined as a Border Enum value
        b3 - southern border of the cell, defined as a Border Enum value
        b4 - western border of the cell, defined as a Border Enum value
        color - the color of the cell, defined as a CellColor Enum value
        respawner - boolean value that, if true, indicates that cell contains a spawnpoint
        ammoCard - ammo tile on the cell
        row - the cell's row on the map
        column - the cell's column on the map
